1. *Nogama* mi nedostaju da hodam. (My legs are missing so I can't walk.)
2. On je igrao bez *nogu*. (He played without legs.)
3. On je trčao *nogama*. (He ran with his legs.)
4. Stavio je ruke na *noge*. (He put his hands on his legs.)
5. Ona je stajala na *nogama*. (She was standing on her legs.)
6. Ona je igrala u parku uz pomoć *nogu*. (She was playing in the park with her legs.)